#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/index.rst:5
msgid "QGIS algorithm provider"
msgstr "Dobavljač QGIS algoritma"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/index.rst:7
msgid ""
"QGIS algorithm provider implements various analysis and geoprocessing "
"operations using mostly only QGIS API. So almost all algorithms from this "
"provider will work \"out of the box\" without any additional configuration."
msgstr ""
"Provajder QGIS algoritama implementira razne operacije analize i geoobrade "
"koristeći uglavnom samo QGIS API. Tako da će skoro svi algoritmi ovog "
"provajdera raditi „odmah po instalaciji“ bez ikakve dodatne konfiguracije"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/index.rst:11
msgid ""
"This provider incorporates some algorithms from plugins and also adds its "
"own algorithms."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj provajder uključuje neke algoritme iz dodataka, a takođe dodaje i "
"sopstvene algoritme."
